Hysteria quickly made her way through the damaged ship. Her small body 
giving her better maneuverability, something she had been thankful for many 
times. She eventually emerged on the bridge, wiping some soot from her face, 
though against her black fur it was nearly impossible to tell she had 
anything on her. She took a quick look around the bridge, her eyes falling 
on the soon to be departing form of her commander, Kluster. Hysteria ran 
over to him, Her pace slowing until it matched his own:
